	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">Dis-moi tout.<delay20 /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /> Qu'est-ce qui a attiré
ton attention?</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Oh?<delay20 /> Je vois<tag a="110" b="0" /> <anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Comme tu voudras.<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Gardons les choses comme elles
