	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Vraiment?<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /> Pas de problème!<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Je comprends.</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />C'est toi qui vois.<delay20 /> <anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Si jamais
tu changes d'avis,<delay8 /> <anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />tu sais où
